1、express locallibrary_02 --view=pug
cd locallibrary_02
npm install
npm install --save-dev nodemon
npm run devstart

2、修改package.json 
   "scripts": {
    "start": "node ./bin/www",
    "devstart": "nodemon ./bin/www"
  },

3、打开http://localhost:3000/或者http://localhost:3000/users

4、Create a new route in /routes/users.js that will display the text "You're so cool" at URL /users/cool/. Test it by running the server and visiting http://localhost:3000/users/cool/ in your browser